<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 21:12:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，德国将在欧盟对中国电动汽车关税的投票中投弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-set-abstain-vote-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-sources-2024-07-12/</link><description>消息人士周五告诉路透社，德国将在欧盟成员国周一就对中国制造的电动汽车征收临时关税的投票中投弃权票，这是对布鲁塞尔里程碑式贸易案支持的首次考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:31:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-set-abstain-vote-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-sources-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，数据中心运营商 Equinix 考虑出售香港资产的少数股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/data-centre-operator-equinix-mulls-minority-stake-sale-hong-kong-assets-sources-2024-07-12/</link><description>两位消息人士称，全球数据中心运营商 Equinix 正在考虑出售其香港设施的少数股权，资产估值约为 20 亿美元，以利用人工智能需求的蓬勃发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 11:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/data-centre-operator-equinix-mulls-minority-stake-sale-hong-kong-assets-sources-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>报道称，意大利将向中国汽车制造商提供已停产的 Stellantis 品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>据《Il Sole 24 Ore》周五报道，意大利政府正在考虑通过法令接管 Stellantis 旗下已不复存在的汽车品牌，并将其提供给中国企业，以鼓励它们在意大利设厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月新增银行贷款未达预期，部分货币指标创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国银行贷款增幅低于预期，而一些关键货币指标创下历史新低，突显出在中国最高领导人准备开会制定长期政策目标之际，世界第二大经济体的需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月对俄罗斯出口增速较上月加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</link><description>海关周五数据显示，6月份中国对俄罗斯以人民币计价的出口同比增长4.76%，高于5月份0.92%的增速，但仍远低于年初两位数的出口增速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾将从中正纪念堂撤走仪仗队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</link><description>文化部周五表示，台湾将撤回前领导人蒋介石纪念馆的军事仪仗队，作为结束“崇拜威权主义”持续努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国队在巴黎横扫金牌，重回乒乓球霸主地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-eye-return-table-tennis-dominance-with-golden-sweep-paris-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国乒乓球队在东京奥运会混双项目上惨败给日本队​​后，将迎战巴黎奥运会，以横扫金牌的方式重新确立在这项运动中的绝对统治地位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-eye-return-table-tennis-dominance-with-golden-sweep-paris-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行周一维持中期贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</link><description>路透调查显示，人们普遍预计中国央行周一将到期贷款展期时将维持中期利率不变，并从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>瓦努阿图总理要求中国银行在维拉港开设分行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</link><description>瓦努阿图总理夏洛特·萨尔瓦伊办公室周五在一份声明中表示，已要求中国银行在这个太平洋岛国开展业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>即时观点：中国6月原油、未锻轧铜进口量同比下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国6月份大豆、煤炭和铁矿石进口量同比增加，而原油、未锻轧铜和稀土进口量下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口高于预期，但进口下降意味着更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国的出口增速创15个月以来最快，这表明制造商在越来越多的贸易伙伴预期征收关税之前提前加载订单，而由于国内需求疲软，进口意外萎缩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责欧盟关于南海的声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国谴责欧盟就南海问题发表的声明，称欧盟无视该问题的历史和客观事实，并“公然”支持其所谓的菲律宾侵犯其主权的行为。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 02:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</link><description>官员周五表示，菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其在有争议的南海的利益，但不希望发生任何冲突，并已与中国就缓解有争议的浅滩的紧张局势达成一致。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>美元兑日元下跌，全球股指上涨，关注降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</link><description>美元兑日元连续第二天大幅下跌，引发人们对日本是否进行干预的质疑，而随着投资者将注意力转向美联储降息，全球股市指数周五上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>商务部长表示中国愿意加强与沙特的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国商务部长周五在一份声明中表示，中国愿与沙特加强实施发展战略，密切贸易和投资交流。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>